# DigiThings — Cursor Legacy Rules
#
# Cursor Agent uses .cursor/rules/digithings.mdc (alwaysApply: true).
# Regenerate with: make agents-init
#
# Quick reference — full rules in AGENTS.md and per-component AGENTS.md files:
#
# Non-negotiables:
#   - Polars only (never pandas)
#   - Pydantic v2 models everywhere
#   - MCP-first tool design
#   - LangGraph supervisor+subgraph orchestration only
#   - LiteLLM routing (caching mandatory)
#   - NautilusTrader for all backtest/optimize
#   - Score ≥8 Security, ≥8 Quality, ≥7 Optimization, ≥9 Accuracy before PR
#   - Never touch live-trading paths without explicit human approval
#
# Before editing any component:
#   1. Read {component}/AGENTS.md  (pre-flight checklist + rules)
#   2. Read {component}/ARCHITECTURE.md  (technical reference)
#
# Backlog: docs/agent-backlog/INDEX.md + GitHub Issues labeled agent-task
# Scoring: docs/scoring/  |  Workflow: docs/agents/AGENT_WORKFLOW.md
